description: Options for fitting content to a frame.

properties.description: Resizes content to fit the frame. Note: Content that is a different size than the frame appears stretched or squeezed.
properties.name: CONTENT_TO_FRAME

properties.description: Centers content in the frame; preserves the frame size as well as content size and proportions. Note: If the content is larger than the frame, content around the edges is obscured.
properties.name: CENTER_CONTENT

properties.description: Resizes content to fit the frame while preserving content proportions. If the content and frame have different proportions, some empty space appears in the frame.
properties.name: PROPORTIONALLY

properties.description: Resizes the frame so it fits the content.
properties.name: FRAME_TO_CONTENT

properties.description: Resizes content to fill the frame while perserving the proportions of the content. If the content and frame have different proportions, some of the content is obscured by the bounding box of the frame.
properties.name: FILL_PROPORTIONALLY

properties.description: Applies the current frame fitting options to the frame and content.
properties.name: APPLY_FRAME_FITTING_OPTIONS

name: FitOptions
